title: Cowboys to play first NFL game in Rio de Janeiro in 2026

sources.name: Yahoo Sports NFL
sources.title: Cowboys to play first NFL game in Rio de Janeiro in 2026
sources.description: The NFL announced that the Dallas Cowboys will play in Rio de Janeiro in 2026, marking the league's first game in the city and third in Brazil.
